know that I can,

00:48:09.650 --> 00:48:13.940
that the time that I've
put in learning my craft

00:48:13.940 --> 00:48:17.040
allows me to actually
do this thing.

00:48:17.040 --> 00:48:21.510
So it is kind of both.

00:48:21.510 --> 00:48:23.840
It's like one of
the things that I

00:48:23.840 --> 00:48:26.300
try to pay attention to when
I start bogging down is like,

00:48:26.300 --> 00:48:27.830
am I bogging down
because there's

00:48:27.830 --> 00:48:30.830
a problem with the story,
or am I bogging down

00:48:30.830 --> 00:48:33.120
because of something external?

00:48:33.120 --> 00:48:37.360
And you handled those
in different ways.

