AUDIENCE: I'm pretty sure
you gave this anecdote

00:51:39.910 --> 00:51:41.860
from your research
where you found out

00:51:41.860 --> 00:51:49.990
that the voice for a computer in
"Star Trek" is really modeled--

00:51:49.990 --> 00:51:51.584
that was really
surprising to me,

00:51:51.584 --> 00:51:52.750
